==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fief
<hw>Fief</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>fief</ets>; of
German origin, and the same word as E. <ets>fee</ets>. See <er>Fee</er>,
and cf. <er>Feud</er>, a tief.]</ety> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>An estate
held of a superior on condition of military service; a fee; a feud. See
under <er>Benefice</er>, <pos>n.</pos>, 2.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

